io.github.whippetdb.memory.api

Class Bytes

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.whippetdb.memory.api.Bytes

  • public class Bytes
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines byte order for all the components of the library in compile-time. To change it, switch between the BytesLE and BytesBE as a superclass.
